title: (x) Zac Brown Band Western-style logo - Mesquite {Ben Shaykin}
content:
Hey guys - I know I’ve seen this font before (a lot recently) but I can not remember the name of it...anybody know?

It’s the main “Zac Brown” font at the top...  
 [http://www.zacbrownband.com/index2.html](http://web.archive.org/web/20070811194439/http:/www.zacbrownband.com/index2.html "http://www.zacbrownband.com/index2.html")

comments.content:
it’s a wider, heavier [Mesquite](http://web.archive.org/web/20070811194439/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/mesquite/).

see also: [tuscans](http://web.archive.org/web/20070811194439/http:/www.myfonts.com/search?search%5Btext%5D=tuscan).
